data.description:
Well maintained brick Cape Cod in South Euclid ready to call home. Updated kitchen with all appliances included. Enclosed porch perfect for morning coffee is located off of the dining area. Home features  2 bedrooms and a full bath on main floor. A third bedroom is located on the second floor along with  a full bath. Partially finished basement with a newer half bath and glass block windows. Washer and dryer included! 
The exterior features a privacy fenced yard, a  2 car garage with newer automatic openers and a recently added carport and widened drive.. perfect  for that extra car, boat, or camper. 
Other updates include roof and gutters (2019), furnace (2018), exterior doors and awnings replaced (2019).
